{"id":"3999","name":"Embed SpringBoard","tagline":"The simplest way to add the `Open SpringBoard` action to your shortcut.","icon":"ios13 c3980825855 g59693","latest":"17476","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1>Embed SpringBoard</h1>\n<hr>\n<p><em><strong>You don't need this on IOS 14 because you can already copy and paste actions. Just get the <a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/2900\">SpringBoard</a> shortcut and copy the action when needed.</strong></em>. </p>\n<hr>\n<p><em>The simplest way to add the </em><em>Open SpringBoard</em><em> action to your shortcut.</em></p>\n<p>This shortcut provides a way to merge the <a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/2900\">SpringBoard</a> shortcut into your own shortcut. So, you shouldn't need run the it externally.</p>\n<h3>Instructions</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Add a Comment action to your shortcut where you want the <strong>Open SpringbBoard</strong> to be inserted. Fill it with the text *SpringBoard*.</li>\n<li>Run this shortcut. When presented with the menu, choose <code>Embed</code>.</li>\n<li>Choose your shortcut.</li>\n<li>When presented with an alert to Create iCloud Link, tap <code>Create Link</code></li>\n<li>You should be presented with the Add Shortcut screen to import your updated shortcut.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>See the screenhots below for the steps above.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Step1\" src=\"https://github.com/supermamon/shortcuts/raw/master/Embed-Springboard/img/step1.png\"><img alt=\"Step2\" src=\"https://github.com/supermamon/shortcuts/raw/master/Embed-Springboard/img/step2.png\"><img alt=\"Step3\" src=\"https://github.com/supermamon/shortcuts/raw/master/Embed-Springboard/img/step3.png\"><img alt=\"Step4\" src=\"https://github.com/supermamon/shortcuts/raw/master/Embed-Springboard/img/step4.png\"><img alt=\"Step5\" src=\"https://github.com/supermamon/shortcuts/raw/master/Embed-Springboard/img/step5.png\"></p>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>1.1.0 - May 31, 2020, 12:15 p.m.</strong></p><p>* Copy iCloud URL on the Clipboar